HEADWORD: Self-asserting
<hw>Self`-as*sert"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>asserting
one's self, or one's own rights or claims; hence, putting one's self
forward in a confident or assuming manner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-assertion</ent>⟦br⟧
